# game/scripts/day14.rpy:10
translate spanish d14a_part_1_a82578ad:

    # "The gates to your house are open, and you're standing in the yard with your back to them, doing maintenance on your precious car."
    "Las puertas de tu casa están abiertas y estás en el patio, dándoles la espalda, haciendo el mantenimiento de tu preciado coche."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:11
translate spanish d14a_part_1_ef42fcda:

    # "At first you don't hear the hesitant steps approaching..."
    "Al principio no escuchas los pasos vacilantes acercándose..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:14
translate spanish d14a_part_1_83b7a7eb:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:20
translate spanish d14a_part_1_47814723:

    # Ka "[persistent.player_name], I am here!"
    Ka "[persistent.player_name], ¡ya estoy aquí!"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:23
translate spanish d14a_part_1_6e037dd7:

    # Z "...?"
    Z "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:26
translate spanish d14a_part_1_52ca87ee:

    # "You put the tools down, caught momentarily off guard by the unexpected presence..."
    "Dejas las herramientas en el suelo, sorprendido momentáneamente por la inesperada presencia..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:32
translate spanish d14a_part_1_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:35
translate spanish d14a_part_1_794bafa5:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Hey, I know you."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Oye, te conozco."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:38
translate spanish d14a_part_1_b12a744d:

    # "You stand up, your body glistening in the blazing sun. Your tall frame gives Kateryna a second of pause, as she hesitates, considering what to say next..."
    "Te pones de pie, con el cuerpo reluciente bajo el sol abrasador. Tu elevada estatura hace que Kateryna se detenga un segundo, mientras duda sobre qué decir a continuación..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:39
translate spanish d14a_part_1_90448559:

    # Z "Welcome, Kateryna."
    Z "Bienvenida, Kateryna."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:42
translate spanish d14a_part_1_e0da345c:

    # Z "We're happy you decided to come join us."
    Z "Nos alegra que hayas decidido unirte a nosotros."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:45
translate spanish d14a_part_1_57a2cdda:

    # "It takes only a few rushed steps for her to join you in the embrace your open arms invited."
    "Bastaron unos pasos apresurados para que se uniera a ti en el abrazo al que tus brazos abiertos invitaban."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:46
translate spanish d14a_part_1_ae7470e2:

    # Ka "I am glad too..."
    Ka "Yo también me alegro..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:49
translate spanish d14a_part_1_062857b3:

    # Z "My wife has already prepared a room for you."
    Z "Mi esposa ya te ha preparado una habitación."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:50
translate spanish d14a_part_1_c8a60e09:

    # Z "She too will be happy to welcome you."
    Z "Ella también se alegrará de recibirte."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:51
translate spanish d14a_part_1_72ed328f:

    # Z "Is that all you bring with you?"
    Z "¿Eso es todo lo que traes contigo?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:52
translate spanish d14a_part_1_377fb0c1:

    # Ka "Yes... Is all. The things from uncle Igor are left. This are things from... old home."
    Ka "Sí... Eso es todo. Quedan las cosas del tío Igor. Son cosas de... la antigua casa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:55
translate spanish d14a_part_1_f17138e6:

    # "She seems a little lost for words..."
    "Parece que no sabe qué decir..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:58
translate spanish d14a_part_1_6c60a9c7:

    # "Returning your embrace, she strokes your back, soft hands tracing the muscles of your shoulders."
    "Devolviéndote el abrazo, te acaricia la espalda, con manos suaves que trazan los músculos de tus hombros."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:61
translate spanish d14a_part_1_7f87dbf0:

    # Ka "I missed you, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ka "Te he echado de menos, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:62
translate spanish d14a_part_1_fcadcced:

    # Ka "Sorry I took long."
    Ka "Perdón por haber tardado tanto."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:65
translate spanish d14a_part_1_fae1df7d:

    # Z "Don't worry about it. You're here now."
    Z "No te preocupes. Ya estás aquí."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:66
translate spanish d14a_part_1_5179709d:

    # Z "There's plenty of time for everything."
    Z "Hay tiempo suficiente para todo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:69
translate spanish d14a_part_1_6f5d0da5:

    # "She lets go of you..."
    "Ella te suelta..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:72
translate spanish d14a_part_1_f238e964:

    # "...and her eyes follow your movements, as she stands with her hands in her lap."
    "... y sus ojos siguen tus movimientos, mientras ella está de pie con las manos en su regazo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:73
translate spanish d14a_part_1_6aa79e10:

    # Z "Hey... Kat?"
    Z "Ey... ¿Kat?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:76
translate spanish d14a_part_1_add0733b:

    # Z "Why don't you go inside? Look for [W] and get settled in."
    Z "¿Por qué no entras? Busca a [W] y acomódate."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:77
translate spanish d14a_part_1_f68b3565:

    # Z "It's a hot day and you've walked a fair distance. Rest a little. I will join you when I am done here."
    Z "Es un día caluroso y has caminado una buena distancia. Descansa un poco. Me reuniré contigo cuando haya terminado aquí."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:79
translate spanish d14a_part_1_08f319ab:

    # Z "Tell [W] that I suggested Emilia draw you a bath. She'll pamper you."
    Z "Dile a [W] que he sugerido a Emilia que te prepare un baño. Ella te mimará."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:81
translate spanish d14a_part_1_74581669:

    # Z "[W] will have [F] draw you a bath as well. She's a servant here, you will like her."
    Z "[W] hará que [F] te prepare un baño también. Ella es una sirvienta aquí, te caerá bien."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:83
translate spanish d14a_part_1_b0aed5cc:

    # Z "[W] will have our servants give you a bath."
    Z "[W] hará que nuestras sirvientas te den un baño."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:86
translate spanish d14a_part_1_a3993a8d:

    # Ka "Thank you. I will see you soon, yes?"
    Ka "Gracias. Te veré pronto, ¿sí?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:89
translate spanish d14a_part_1_3a08cc2f:

    # Z "Yes, in less than an hour, promise."
    Z "Sí, en menos de una hora, te lo prometo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:92
translate spanish d14a_part_1_70d036ac:

    # "After cleaning and servicing your vehicle, you pack up your tools and go back inside."
    "Tras limpiar y revisar tu vehículo, recoges tus herramientas y vuelves a entrar."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:95
translate spanish d14a_part_1_f39a3ff6:

    # Z "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:100
translate spanish d14a_part_1_a36f498b:

    # W "Hey hot guy."
    W "Ey tío bueno."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:101
translate spanish d14a_part_1_0395d470:

    # Z "Hey wife."
    Z "Ey esposa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:104
translate spanish d14a_part_1_5a8adac2:

    # W "I wanted to speak about our new house member, if you don't mind."
    W "Quería hablar de nuestro nueva miembro de la casa, si no te importa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:107
translate spanish d14a_part_1_45a1820c:

    # Z "How is she liking her bath?"
    Z "¿Le está gustando el baño?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:110
translate spanish d14a_part_1_023bb872:

    # "She sits down..."
    "Ella se sienta..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:111
translate spanish d14a_part_1_c7488d93:

    # W "Mh... she's quite shy."
    W "Mh... Es bastante tímida."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:113
translate spanish d14a_part_1_00b5097b:

    # W "But Emilia is disciplined and caring. They will like each other."
    W "Pero Emilia es disciplinada y cariñosa. Se caerán bien."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:115
translate spanish d14a_part_1_6173e27e:

    # W "[fairy_name] on the other hand... let's just say I had to remind her that she's just supposed to give a bath."
    W "[fairy_name], por otro lado... digamos que tuve que recordarle que solo se supone que debe dar un baño."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:116
translate spanish d14a_part_1_e1a21489:

    # W "She instantly took a liking for Kateryna."
    W "Ella al instante se encariñó con Kateryna."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:118
translate spanish d14a_part_1_ae365890:

    # W "Emilia and [fairy_name] are taking good care of her. It's a good thing Emilia is there to limit [fairy_name]'s... exuberance."
    W "Emilia y [fairy_name] están cuidando muy bien de ella. Menos mal que Emilia está ahí para limitar la... exuberancia de [fairy_name]."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:122
translate spanish d14a_part_1_8b3393aa:

    # W "I also let [S] and [A] know to join us in an hour."
    W "También avisé a [S] y a [A] para que se unieran a nosotros en una hora."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:125
translate spanish d14a_part_1_0fc18dba:

    # Z "Yeah... let's bring them together so we can get the introduction done."
    Z "Sí... reunámoslas para que podamos hacer la presentación."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:130
translate spanish d14a_part_1_acac0172:

    # W "Most of our girls already know Kateryna anyway."
    W "De todos modos, la mayoría de nuestras chicas ya conocen a Kateryna."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:133
translate spanish d14a_part_1_ff68121b:

    # W "And [S] won't mind..."
    W "Y [S] no se molestará..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:134
translate spanish d14a_part_1_f513ef38:

    # W "Hmm... husband...?"
    W "Hmm... ¿marido...?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:135
translate spanish d14a_part_1_4357638a:

    # Z "Have I told you already that you look lovely today..."
    Z "¿Te he dicho ya que hoy estás preciosa?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:138
translate spanish d14a_part_1_e791e48d:

    # W "As much as I appreciate it... I think you have someone else you should focus on tonight."
    W "Por mucho que lo aprecie... creo que deberías centrarte en alguien más esta noche."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:139
translate spanish d14a_part_1_2fcd40ef:

    # W "...and I know for a fact she wants your focus on her even more."
    W "... y sé a ciencia cierta que quiere que te concentres aún más en ella."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:147
translate spanish d14a_part_1_438621b0:

    # W "Most of our girls already know Kateryna anyway. And [S] won't mind her one bit."
    W "La mayoría de nuestras chicas ya conocen a Kateryna de todos modos. Y a [S] no le importará lo más mínimo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:148
translate spanish d14a_part_1_e9b5b4d6:

    # W "Especially not once she tries her cooking."
    W "Sobre todo cuando pruebe su cocina."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:151
translate spanish d14a_part_1_b2bec007:

    # Z "Looks like your days of cooking are finally over after all."
    Z "Parece que, después de todo, tus días de cocinera han terminado."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:159
translate spanish d14a35_83b7a7eb:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:162
translate spanish d14a35_e893871d:

    # Ka "Um... [W]... I can't find my skirt. Did you put it in the wash-...?"
    Ka "Um... [W]... No encuentro mi falda. ¿La has metido en el lavade...?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:165
translate spanish d14a35_de791e17:

    # Ka "Oh, hi [persistent.player_name]!"
    Ka "Oh, ¡hola [persistent.player_name]!"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:168
translate spanish d14a35_07008a9d:

    # W "Hey Kateryna, join us!"
    W "Ey Kateryna, ¡únete a nosotros!"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:171
translate spanish d14a35_98e89eef:

    # "She approaches you both."
    "Se acerca a los dos."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:174
translate spanish d14a35_cf31c13a:

    # Ka "Hey..."
    Ka "Ey..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:180
translate spanish d14a35_a8fde11d:

    # W "I don't think she needs that skirt, after all."
    W "No creo que necesite esa falda, después de todo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:183
translate spanish d14a35_d30a5457:

    # "You take a look at the new member of your house..."
    "Echas un vistazo al nuevo miembro de tu casa..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:184
translate spanish d14a35_d52f8a87:

    # Z "I am sure you know best, [W]."
    Z "Estoy seguro de que tú lo sabes mejor, [W]."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:187
translate spanish d14a35_6d6f5770:

    # Z "Hey girl, you can sit down if you want."
    Z "Ey chica, puedes sentarte si quieres."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:190
translate spanish d14a35_493bf9a5:

    # "Encouraged by your friendliness, she sits down on your lap..."
    "Animada por tu amabilidad, se sienta en tu regazo..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:192
translate spanish d14a35_3c15519b:

    # Ka "Thank you for bath... Emilia is very kind."
    Ka "Gracias por el baño... Emilia es muy amable."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:194
translate spanish d14a35_ac8d1c6d:

    # Ka "Thank you for bath. [F] is very kind, but she is bit handsy. {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    Ka "Gracias por el baño. [F] es muy amable, pero es un poco manoseadora. {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:196
translate spanish d14a35_ef1747d7:

    # Ka "Thank you for bath. Emilia and [F] are very kind. {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    Ka "Gracias por el baño. Emilia y [F] son muy amables. {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:197
translate spanish d14a35_8fc5382b:

    # Ka "I even fell asleep. Very relaxed. A bath... last time for bath like this was, back in old country. More water there."
    Ka "Incluso me dormí. Muy relajada. Un baño... la última vez que me bañé así fue en el viejo país. Allí había más agua."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:200
translate spanish d14a35_5b3b3c4f:

    # W "You will soon become a part of this household, Kateryna. We take care of each other here."
    W "Pronto formarás parte de esta casa, Kateryna. Aquí nos cuidamos unos a otros."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:201
translate spanish d14a35_4f740159:

    # W "You too will have ways to bring joy and comfort to the family. We have tasted your cooking before..."
    W "Tú también tendrás formas de llevar alegría y consuelo a la familia. Ya hemos probado antes tu cocina..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:202
translate spanish d14a35_5c6c9844:

    # W "But first, we should introduce you properly to the others."
    W "Pero primero, debemos presentarte adecuadamente a los demás."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:205
translate spanish d14a35_cb5ae56a:

    # Ka "Introduce...?"
    Ka "¿Presentar...?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:206
translate spanish d14a35_fb3b8d9e:

    # W "Oh yes! It's a custom in Zeta."
    W "¡Oh, sí! Es una costumbre en Zeta."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:207
translate spanish d14a35_6d08401d:

    # W "We don't stand too much on the many traditions, but some occasions deserve a little formality. Don't worry though..."
    W "No somos muy partidarios de las muchas tradiciones, pero algunas ocasiones merecen un poco de formalidad. Pero no te preocupes..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:208
translate spanish d14a35_9d7bf3a4:

    # W "It will not take too long and we will walk you through it. If you're joining the house, it should be properly acknowledged by everybody, don't you think?"
    W "No llevará demasiado tiempo y te guiaremos a través de ello. Si te unes a la casa, debería ser debidamente reconocida por todos, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:211
translate spanish d14a35_9cc6972f:

    # Ka "Yes... it make sense."
    Ka "Sí... tiene sentido."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:212
translate spanish d14a35_95ff85d3:

    # Zt "Man. I should thank Igor again once this is all over."
    Zt "Hombre. Debería volver a dar las gracias a Igor cuando todo esto acabe."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:213
translate spanish d14a35_3d303599:

    # Zt "He really brought me someone special."
    Zt "Realmente me ha traído a alguien especial."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:216
translate spanish d14a35_eaea5f2a:

    # Zt "Everyone in this house will love her. She's friendly, kind, humble..."
    Zt "Todos en esta casa la adorarán. Es simpática, amable, humilde..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:217
translate spanish d14a35_6a45098b:

    # Zt "...and I will make sure she won't regret coming here."
    Zt "... y me aseguraré de que no se arrepienta de haber venido."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:220
translate spanish d14a35_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:226
translate spanish d14a35_d5542731:

    # Z "Everybody... You probably know why I've gathered you."
    Z "Todas... Seguramente sabéis por qué os he reunido."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:227
translate spanish d14a35_3ded1c47:

    # Z "It is time to introduce a new member of the house."
    Z "Ha llegado el momento de presentar a un nuevo miembro de la casa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:228
translate spanish d14a35_ccdf37d2:

    # Z "Kateryna travelled a long way; all the way from the northern lands, across the mediterranean sea."
    Z "Kateryna ha hecho un largo viaje; desde las tierras del norte, a través del mar Mediterráneo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:229
translate spanish d14a35_9dcc8b1a:

    # Z "She is my good friend Igor's niece, so in a way, by association, she was already a friend to this family."
    Z "Es la sobrina de mi buen amigo Igor, así que en cierto modo, por asociación, ya era amiga de esta familia."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:241
translate spanish d14a35_c8eb01cc:

    # Z "I know that I can trust you all to treat her with respect and that you will grow to love her with the same devotion you have towards one another."
    Z "Yo sé que puedo confiar en todas para tratarla con respeto y que llegarán a quererla con la misma devoción que tenéis entre vosotras."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:242
translate spanish d14a35_12202709:

    # Z "I know you well and expect nothing less than open arms and hearts towards this young woman who has freely chosen to join us."
    Z "Os conozco bien y no espero nada menos que brazos y corazones abiertos hacia esta joven que ha elegido unirse libremente a nosotros."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:254
translate spanish d14a35_cf448dd2:

    # Z "Kateryna is kind hearted, diligent, well spirited, and some of you already know that she's a very good cook."
    Z "Kateryna es de buen corazón, diligente y de buen espíritu... y algunas de vosotras ya sabéis que es muy buena cocinera."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:255
translate spanish d14a35_f2523b23:

    # Z "Every one of us serves the house. Just like you do, so will she, and in turn, you will serve her."
    Z "Cada uno de nosotros sirve a la Casa. Igual que vosotras, ella también lo hará y, a su vez, la serviréis."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:261
translate spanish d14a35_8e396b1b:

    # Z "[A]... You and Kateryna already are acquainted with each other. Don't think you can take advantage of her, though. I will be keeping an eye on you."
    Z "[A]... Kateryna y tú ya os conocéis. Sin embargo, no creas que puedes aprovecharte de ella. Te vigilaré."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:262
translate spanish d14a35_55e77e0b:

    # Z "Remember that Kateryna is your equal... Treat her like a sister."
    Z "Recuerda que Kateryna es tu igual... Trátala como a una hermana."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:266
translate spanish d14a35_b303fcc4:

    # Z "Emilia. Make sure you assist Kateryna in anything she needs."
    Z "Emilia. Asegúrate de ayudar a Kateryna en todo lo que necesite."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:267
translate spanish d14a35_c791aa4c:

    # Z "She will be a boon to this family, and be deserving of your service."
    Z "Será una bendición para esta familia y merecerá tu servicio."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:270
translate spanish d14a35_6987e099:

    # E "Of course, Master. I shall be of service."
    E "Por supuesto, Maestro. Estaré a su servicio."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:279
translate spanish d14a35_95582e51:

    # Z "[F]. Serve her like you would serve me or any of the women of this house."
    Z "[F]. Sírvela como me servirías a mí o a cualquiera de las mujeres de esta casa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:280
translate spanish d14a35_cf9543f2:

    # Z "And... give Kateryna some assistance settling in."
    Z "Y... ayuda a Kateryna a instalarse."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:286
translate spanish d14a35_3af08117:

    # F "Yes, Master."
    F "Sí, Amo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:290
translate spanish d14a35_e49acbd3:

    # Z "You will not need to do everything on your own, Kateryna. My servants are there for you."
    Z "No tendrás que hacerlo todo tú sola, Kateryna. Mis sirvientas estarán a tu disposición."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:291
translate spanish d14a35_b8da1210:

    # Z "It is their duty to serve the members of this house, and from this day onwards, that includes you."
    Z "Su deber es servir a los miembros de esta casa y, a partir de hoy, eso te incluye a ti."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:292
translate spanish d14a35_50b32228:

    # Ka "Thank you..."
    Ka "Gracias..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:304
translate spanish d14a35_cb4b4165:

    # Z "This house is special, and not just in that it is special to me... we trust each other. You have seen the dangers of the wastelands and the hardships of the desert."
    Z "Esta casa es especial, y no solo en el sentido de que es especial para mí... confiamos los unos en los otros. Has visto los peligros de los páramos y las penurias del desierto."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:305
translate spanish d14a35_50027368:

    # Z "This house stands on the edge, between civilisation and the hostile world. It is a bastion for those who call it home."
    Z "Esta casa se encuentra en el límite, entre la civilización y el mundo hostil. Es un bastión para quienes la llaman hogar."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:306
translate spanish d14a35_306fc8f3:

