    # Z "So, she herself has told me that she would like to remain a servant in this house."
    Z "Entonces, ella misma me ha dicho que le gustaría seguir siendo una sirvienta en esta casa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3284
translate spanish d14g_19e43764:

    # Z "[F] is a kind soul, who is committed to do her best to serve our House and harbours no ill intent."
    Z "[F] es una persona amable, comprometida a hacer lo mejor para servir a nuestra Casa y no alberga malas intenciones."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3290
translate spanish d14g_ff103a7b:

    # Z "[F] will be a servant to the House, with the duties, responsibilities and rights that this position entails."
    Z "[F] será una sirvienta de la Casa, con los deberes, responsabilidades y derechos que conlleva esta posición."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3291
translate spanish d14g_925192ad:

    # Z "Consider this, however: the [F] you have observed and toyed with in the basement is no longer. [F] has emerged from the basement, and joins us of her own free will."
    Z "Sin embargo, considera esto: la [F] que has observado y con la que has jugado en el sótano ya no existe. [F] ha salido del sótano y se une a nosotros por voluntad propia."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3292
translate spanish d14g_6624cb3e:

    # Z "She is not the broken creature that first came here, and I will not have you treat her as anything less than what she is."
    Z "No es la criatura rota que llegó aquí por primera vez, y no permitiré que la trates como menos de lo que es."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3293
translate spanish d14g_f20ce48b:

    # Z "Make her life in this household worth living; let her be a servant, but let's also give her the chance to fully heal."
    Z "Haz que su vida en este hogar merezca la pena; que sea una sirvienta, pero también démosle la oportunidad de curarse por completo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3297
translate spanish d14g_a93b7770:

    # Z "[E], as you are the maid, she will be under your responsibility and tutelage."
    Z "[E], como eres la criada, ella estará bajo tu responsabilidad y tutela."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3298
translate spanish d14g_443f6f00:

    # Z "Teach her all that she needs to learn."
    Z "Enséñale todo lo que necesita aprender."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3301
translate spanish d14g_d166f266:

    # E "Yes, of course, Master. I will take good care of her."
    E "Sí, por supuesto, Amo. Cuidaré bien de ella."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3304
translate spanish d14g_5ac0da1b:

    # Z "Very well, I trust that you will."
    Z "Muy bien, confío en que lo harás."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3307
translate spanish d14g_7ea6997e:

    # Z "Now that this is done,..."
    Z "Ahora que esto está hecho,..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3308
translate spanish d14g_04db4f22:

    # Z "[A] will show you to your quarters. Are you ready for a new beginning, [F]?"
    Z "[A] te mostrará tus aposentos. ¿Estás lista para un nuevo comienzo, [F]?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3311
translate spanish d14g_e2bf7639:

    # F "Yes, Master. Thank you."
    F "Sí, Amo. Gracias, Señor."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3327
translate spanish d14g_3123836a:

    # Z "Girls, we have come together to introduce a new member to the household."
    Z "Chicas, nos hemos reunido para presentaros a un nuevo miembro a este hogar."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3331
translate spanish d14g_ee55200a:

    # Z "Everyone, we have come together to introduce a new member to this household."
    Z "Todos, nos hemos reunido para presentaros a un nuevo miembro de esta casa."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3332
translate spanish d14g_c5319af2_1:

    # Z "I will try to make it quick this time, but there are some things you need to know about her."
    Z "Intentaré ser rápido esta vez, pero hay algunas cosas que debéis saber acerca de ella."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3333
translate spanish d14g_722cf5b4_1:

    # Z "You have already met her, although under different circumstances."
    Z "Ya la habéis conocido, aunque en otras circunstancias."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3334
translate spanish d14g_8b6045eb:

    # Z "I will try to make this quick, but there are some things that need to be said."
    Z "Intentaré hacerlo rápido, pero hay algunas cosas que deben decirse."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3337
translate spanish d14g_3a344a9e_1:

    # Z "[F], come to me."
    Z "[F], ven hacia mí."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3343
translate spanish d14g_60bbd2ee:

    # Z "Girls, you know that when I took [F] in from the Decayed, she was broken, reduced to a feral creature acting purely out of a constant fear of death."
    Z "Chicas, sabéis que cuando recogí a [F] de la Decadencia, estaba destrozada, reducida a una criatura salvaje que actuaba únicamente por un miedo constante a la muerte."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3344
translate spanish d14g_8e30f8c1:

    # Z "In time however, it was revealed that her condition was a refuge, a temporary state from which she was able to recover."
    Z "Sin embargo, con el tiempo se reveló que su condición era un refugio, un estado temporal del que podía recuperarse."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3345
translate spanish d14g_d34f0adf:

    # Z "Thanks to [W]'s ministrations and dedication, you are back on your feet now, [F], and we are happy to see how you have turned a new page."
    Z "Gracias a las atenciones y a la dedicación de [W], ya te has recuperado, [F], y nos alegra ver cómo has pasado página."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3351
translate spanish d14g_e7913b4a:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3357
translate spanish d14g_f446b74a:

    # Z "[F] will be our new servant. She has been the slave of the Decayed for years on end, spent primarily in sexual servitude."
    Z "[F] será nuestra nueva criada. Ha sido esclava de los Decaídos durante años, principalmente en servidumbre sexual."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3358
translate spanish d14g_538c82b4:

    # Z "[F] will remain a slave, but she has many things to learn still about what the duties and tasks of a slave are in more civilised circumstances."
    Z "[F] seguirá siendo una esclava, pero todavía tiene mucho que aprender sobre las tareas y deberes de una esclava en circunstancias más civilizadas."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3359
translate spanish d14g_710d74ab:

    # Z "She will learn what services each of you can and will request off her, and I am sure you will all give her the time to adapt to this new life."
    Z "Aprenderá qué servicios puede y quiere solicitarle cada uno de vosotros, y estoy segura de que todos le daréis tiempo para adaptarse a esta nueva vida."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3360
translate spanish d14g_d01bd781:

    # Z "Let us show her a household where a slave is not a creature without her own dignity."
    Z "Enseñémosle un hogar donde una esclava no es una criatura sin dignidad propia."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3364
translate spanish d14g_b735005b:

    # Z "Emilia. Your responsibility will be to train [F] and discipline her when appropriate."
    Z "Emilia. Tu responsabilidad será entrenar a [F] y disciplinarla cuando sea apropiado."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3365
translate spanish d14g_90bfaee5:

    # Z "However I expect that [F] will be a kind and eager servant. You will like her."
    Z "Sin embargo, espero que [F] sea una sirvienta amable y ansiosa. Te caerá bien."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3368
translate spanish d14g_f5f9e563:

    # E "Yes, Master. I will make sure you will be pleased with her service."
    E "Sí, amo. Me aseguraré de que estés satisfecho con su servicio."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3376
translate spanish d14g_fea9484d:

    # Z "That should be everything for now. [A], you will show her to her quarters."
    Z "Eso debería ser todo por ahora. [A], la acompañarás a sus aposentos."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3377
translate spanish d14g_821a048a:

    # A "Yup! Will do!"
    A "Sí. ¡Lo haré!"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3383
translate spanish d14g_3a344a9e_2:

    # Z "[F], come to me."
    Z "[F], ven hacia mí."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3386
translate spanish d14g_f24a203a:

    # "You wrap your arms around her neck and pull her in, as she faces the household..."
    "Le rodeas el cuello con los brazos y tiras de ella, mientras se enfrenta a la casa..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3387
translate spanish d14g_4266a93a:

    # Z "Everyone here knows our new slave already. [F] has been in the basement for long enough that you have all had a chance to see her for what she is."
    Z "Todos los presentes conocéis ya a nuestra nueva esclava. [F] lleva en el sótano el tiempo suficiente para que todos hayáis tenido la oportunidad de verla tal como es."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3388
translate spanish d14g_204fb91d:

    # Z "Before she arrived, she behaved recklessly, a ravenous creature led only by fear and her basest instincts. Since then, much has changed."
    Z "Antes de que llegara, se comportaba de forma temeraria, una criatura voraz guiada sólo por el miedo y sus instintos más bajos. Desde entonces, muchas cosas han cambiado."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3394
translate spanish d14g_3aaea722:

    # Z "Thanks to the strict discipline instilled by [W] and me, she has left that version of herself in the past and is now ready to become my new slave."
    Z "Gracias a la estricta disciplina inculcada por [W] y por mí, ha dejado esa versión de sí misma en el pasado y ahora está preparada para convertirse en mi nueva esclava."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3396
translate spanish d14g_a841f3c7:

    # Z "She may not be as disciplined and focused as Emilia, but, well.. that was never going to be the case."
    Z "Puede que no sea tan disciplinada y centrada como Emilia, pero, bueno... ése nunca iba a ser el caso."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3397
translate spanish d14g_c121f958:

    # Z "[S], you haven't had a great deal of direct experience of her... skills, but I am sure that in time this will change. You will see, she will make a good little servant"
    Z "[S], no has tenido mucha experiencia directa con sus... habilidades, pero estoy seguro de que con el tiempo esto cambiará. Verás, se convertirá en una buena pequeña sirvienta."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3398
translate spanish d14g_5f18028b:

    # S "I can imagine."
    S "Puedo imaginar."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3401
translate spanish d14g_63e73e57:

    # Z "Now, I won't lie to you. [F] is not here because of her character, or her intelligence."
    Z "No te mentiré. [F] no está aquí por su carácter, ni por su inteligencia."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3402
translate spanish d14g_f82262bd:

    # Z "I am not sure whether she truly processes anything of what we are talking about."
    Z "No estoy seguro de si ella realmente comprende algo de lo que estamos hablando."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3403
translate spanish d14g_9f5ec8a1:

    # Z "The one redeeming quality she possesses is an insatiable appetite and talent for sex."
    Z "La única cualidad redentora que posee es un apetito insaciable y talento para el sexo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3404
translate spanish d14g_9bb314ef:

    # Z "Isn't that right, [F]?"
    Z "¿No es cierto, [F]?"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3407
translate spanish d14g_3af08117:

    # F "Yes, Master."
    F "Sí, Amo."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3410
translate spanish d14g_25ff254c:

    # A "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    A "{i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3414
translate spanish d14g_d7969a44:

    # Z "Emilia. In my absence, it is your responsibility to be to train [F] into at least some basic skills and discipline her when she doesn't learn."
    Z "Emilia. En mi ausencia, es tu responsabilidad entrenar a [F] al menos en algunas habilidades básicas y disciplinarla cuando no aprenda."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3415
translate spanish d14g_d30b3f5e:

    # Z "Now that you know what drives her the most, I am sure you will find ways to stimulate her into learning."
    Z "Ahora que sabes qué es lo que más la motiva, estoy seguro de que encontrarás la forma de estimularla para que aprenda."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3418
translate spanish d14g_e95d4e45:

    # E "Yes, Master. I will make sure you are pleased with her service."
    E "Sí, Amo. Me aseguraré de que estés satisfecho con su servicio."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3426
translate spanish d14g_bdc6f618:

    # Z "As our slave, [F] will do everything you ask off her, that much we have been able to teach her; but then, it was easy. I suspect she always was a little perverted to begin with."
    Z "Como nuestra esclava, [F] hará todo lo que le pidas, eso es lo que hemos logrado enseñarle; pero bueno, fue fácil. Sospecho que siempre fue un poco pervertida para empezar."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3427
translate spanish d14g_6ccf306e:

    # Z "Anyway, you may have your ways with her. I am sure she will not object."
    Z "De todos modos, puedes hacerlo a tu manera con ella. Estoy seguro de que ella no se opondrá."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3433
translate spanish d14g_1bd06a7f:

    # Z "[A], I know that look. You may take [F] to the quarters next."
    Z "[A], conozco esa mirada. Puedes llevar a [F] a los aposentos de al lado."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3439
translate spanish d14g_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3440
translate spanish d14g_8a711fb8:

    # "She smiles mischievously..."
    "Ella sonríe con picardía..."

# game/scripts/day14.rpy:3441
translate spanish d14g_54a13311:

    # Z "That will be all."
    Z "Eso es todo."

