    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2258
    old "\"A cylinder made of metal and glass, glowing with ominous light.\""
    new "\"Un cilindro hecho de metal y vidrio, brillando con una luz ominosa.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2258
    old "\"She found a fair number of things.\""
    new "\"Ella encontró un buen número de cosas.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2258
    old "\"(Lie) She was not.\""
    new "\"(Mentira) No lo hizo.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2304
    old "\"The remains of a dead civlization.\""
    new "\"Los restos de una civilización muerta.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2304
    old "\"Cairo's mist is spreading unusually far outside the city.\""
    new "\"La niebla del Cairo se está extendiendo inusualmente lejos fuera de la ciudad.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2304
    old "\"Possibilities, secrets and hidden treasures.\""
    new "\"Posibilidades, secretos y tesoros ocultos.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2469
    old "\"Why would I...\""
    new "\"¿Por qué iba a...?\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2469
    old "\"I could tell the Palace about this.\""
    new "\"Podría informar al Palacio sobre esto.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:2499
    old "It seems the red mist of Cairo and the holy storms we witness every now and then both share a man-made origin. But to what end?\nI wanted answers, and I got at least some of them, but at the same time more questions arise. The artifact seems to be an important part of this, though I don't yet know exactly how.\nAbrax was quick to share what he knows and invited me to see him again. But for what purpose? Only time will tell."
    new "Parece que tanto la niebla roja del Cairo como las tormentas sagradas que presenciamos de vez en cuando comparten un origen humano. Pero ¿con qué fin?\nQuería respuestas, y al menos obtuve algunas, pero al mismo tiempo surgen más preguntas. El artefacto parece ser una parte importante, aunque aún no sé exactamente cómo.\nAbrax se apresuró a compartir lo que sabe y me invitó a verle de nuevo. ¿Pero con qué propósito? Sólo el tiempo lo dirá."

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3008
    old "I like when they show spirit"
    new "Me gusta cuando muestran espíritu"

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3008
    old "What an insufferable bitch"
    new "Menuda zorra insufrible"

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3190
    old "\"I'm sorry that happened to you.\""
    new "\"Siento lo que te ha pasado.\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3190
    old "\"You didn't see any of this coming?!\""
    new "\"¡¿No viste venir nada de esto?!\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3190
    old "\"At least you still have one arm, and your tits...\""
    new "\"Al menos aún tienes un brazo, y tus tetas...\""

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3227
    old "Casanova may be unhinged, but he is not a bad storyteller.\nI now know about his and Zion's backstory, and how a tribe that names itself \"Sekhmet's Legion\" is connected to them.\nZion said that she will contemplate about what to do with the new threat."
    new "Puede que Casanova esté desquiciado, pero no es un mal narrador.\nAhora conozco su historia y la de Zion, y cómo una tribu que se hace llamar \"Legión de Sekhmet\" está relacionada con ellos.\nZion dijo que reflexionará sobre qué hacer con la nueva amenaza."

    # game/scripts/day14.rpy:3335
    old "Commend her"
    new "Elógiala"
